Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.13,0:41:04.71,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躓いて 転んでたら置いてかれんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.91,0:41:12.19,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泥水の中を今日もよろめきながら進む
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.45,0:41:18.93,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}汚れちまった僕のセカイ　浮いた話など無い
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.17,0:41:25.80,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}染み付いた孤独論理 拭えなくなっている
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.82,0:41:35.11,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}試されてまでもここにいることを決めたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.29,0:41:41.26,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}呪文のように「仕方ない」とつぶやいていた
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.31,0:41:44.64,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}積み上げたものぶっ壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.69,0:41:48.29,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}身に着けたもの取っ払って
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.37,0:41:55.54,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}止め処ない血と汗で渇いた脳を潤せ
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.57,0:42:02.72,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの頃の僕らはきっと全力で少年だった
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.72,0:42:07.95,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}セカイを開くのは誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.75,0:42:16.17,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遊ぶこと忘れてたら老いて枯れんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.63,0:42:23.15,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここんとこは仕事オンリー　笑えなくなっている
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.15,0:42:32.38,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ガラクタの中に輝いてた物がいっぱいあったろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.51,0:42:38.55,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大切なもの全て埋もれてしまう前に
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.58,0:42:42.09,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さえぎるものはぶっ飛ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.09,0:42:45.55,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まとわりつくものかわして
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.57,0:42:52.87,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}止め処ない血と汗で渇いた心臓潤せ
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.88,0:42:59.85,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの頃の僕らはきっと全力で少年だった
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.88,0:43:04.97,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}怯えてたら何も生まれない
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.13,0:41:04.71,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跌跌撞撞失足後 就此被拋下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.91,0:41:12.19,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今天 仍在困境中搖晃前進
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.45,0:41:18.93,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我的世界已經污穢 好事從不出現
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.17,0:41:25.80,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}根深蒂固的孤獨法則 始終抹不去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.82,0:41:35.11,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘗試再多 眼前的一切仍無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.29,0:41:41.26,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}宛如咒語的「無可奈何」只能心中默念
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.31,0:41:44.64,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已累積的全部毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.69,0:41:48.29,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}加諸我身的剝光除卻
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.37,0:41:55.54,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}滋潤飢渴大腦的是無可遏止的汗與血
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.57,0:42:02.72,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}當時的我們 卯足全力沖少年
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.72,0:42:07.95,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}開創世界的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.75,0:42:16.17,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘了遊戲人間 開始枯老凋萎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.63,0:42:23.15,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最近滿腦子只有工作 笑容也不見
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.15,0:42:32.38,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破銅爛鐵中 曾經有許多燦爛出現
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.51,0:42:38.55,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在我們「珍惜的一切」全部埋葬之前
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.58,0:42:42.09,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}壓抑困厄要衝破釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.09,0:42:45.55,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}糾纏煩擾都閃躲奔逃
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.57,0:42:52.87,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}滋潤飢渴心臟的是無可遏止的汗與血
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.88,0:42:59.85,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}當時的我們 卯足全力沖少年
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.88,0:43:04.97,CMCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}害怕 就闖不出一片天

Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我就是個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和女生交往也馬上就會分手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她養的狗狂吠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那之後 我就不敢再去她家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會途中 被流氓耍也什麼都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而被救的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也沒去成住在高層的她家的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和女生談戀愛馬上就會分手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…是在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:04:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對開始交往的女孩從沒好好表達過愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我最可悲之處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也交到了新女友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要好好對她說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算今天和他分手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是談了不久就告吹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害了他最重視之人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有他突然逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也沒見面的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我醒來發現他已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣 戀愛總在萌芽時就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為他做的一切 也總是事與願違
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 你真是沒緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有真正被愛過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再喜歡人家 那樣是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在交往的男朋友 悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我對他說喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總是沒什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想結束這單相思的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想把今天的約會作為美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…再也不想有那樣的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打扮得挺漂亮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會嗎 可別遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝蓋沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛在家門口跌倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大的事我什麼都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴真是個不可思議的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的衣服很適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說這種話的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要好好表達…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大不是也打扮了嗎 很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 花了點心思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之前先送禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的不是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號真差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是寵物店的大橋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 出了點差錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 差錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經把盒子打開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你訂購的兔子還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕可能是小型驢鑽進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…小型驢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽進去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動物會自己做那種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我就拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 千萬別打開盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢是種很難管的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒濕 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個送給他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我撿到丟了的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好像是城東3丁目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先幫保管下 我會再給你打電話的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別打開盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢是種很難管的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小型驢）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淘氣蛋 無法預測他的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會咬人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很暴力需多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼賠我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 還是不想就這樣結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 這樣很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著前面走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便把這些也洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是做這種事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不知道他的郵箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您帶來的那位…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我是撿到手機的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是留言中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 沒什麼 很苦惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也不知道工作什麼時候能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我給她送過去吧 反正我開車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是我帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愛的包淋濕了 手機又丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大送我這種怪東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 知道今天是什麼日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是剛剛接到聯繫的山田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿到你的手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 順便給你送來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不請自來會不會給你造成麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也不知道工作什麼時候能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面碰頭比較困難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻煩您特地送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口有點渴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請我喝點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你男朋友有打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有留言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 好像搞錯把小型驢裝進去了 難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫小型驢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:21:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 給我打…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個無可救藥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優柔寡斷 膽小怕事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又傻傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你更讓人覺得可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 好像還什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢 停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是新宮之阪 在新宮之阪停車
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實美希 和男朋友吵架沒地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:23:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後… 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在有在交往的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不知道能不能說在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 和你已經…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才開始你一個人不停地說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會夜襲你的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有那個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.84,0:24:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們為什麼分手的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.21,0:24:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 有交往過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.24,0:24:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.83,0:25:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 再見一次面確認下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.57,0:25:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被說了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.32,0:25:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要通心粉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.34,0:25:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要海鮮燴飯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.82,0:25:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 炒飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.51,0:25:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.13,0:25:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍後來為您服務
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.97,0:25:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.75,0:25:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好像很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.70,0:25:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大 今天突然不見了很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.81,0:26:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們再見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.85,0:26:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為晚了所以給你發了短信
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.93,0:26:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了 外面下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.18,0:26:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.66,0:26:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屋裡的是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.20,0:26:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 一定是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.97,0:26:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.81,0:26:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓悠大嚇一大跳 所以要乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.49,0:26:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.99,0:26:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.98,0:26:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是路上小心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.55,0:27:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像還要花點時間嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.89,0:27:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.72,0:27:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 把鑰匙放郵箱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.46,0:27:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鈴聲是悠大打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.38,0:27:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.14,0:27:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.46,0:27:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.60,0:27:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.62,0:27:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.52,0:27:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.00,0:27:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.69,0:27:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我好擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.15,0:27:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機掉了 沒法跟你聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.64,0:27:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那個盒子裡裝著一個叫小型驢的動物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.07,0:27:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 裝著
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.97,0:27:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.88,0:28:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞錯了 沒有胡鬧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.81,0:28:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.68,0:28:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.02,0:28:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.38,0:28:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.15,0:28:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美希
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.97,0:28:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這個人是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.76,0:28:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.07,0:28:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.48,0:28:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天不是也和男人在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.85,0:28:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.89,0:28:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆不是在耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.71,0:28:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.51,0:28:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.73,0:28:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.88,0:28:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.31,0:28:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有被真正愛過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男朋友和好了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.54,0:29:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說我只愛你 快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.79,0:29:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.52,0:29:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這個盒子是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.55,0:29:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友的禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.78,0:29:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.36,0:29:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.54,0:29:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.67,0:30:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.84,0:30:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.94,0:30:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事必須要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.35,0:30:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我昨天把要送給悠大的禮物弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.74,0:30:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以的話 打工結束後繼續昨天的約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.39,0:30:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有小型驢就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.70,0:30:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點麻煩 但是只好寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.28,0:30:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天聽我說了很多話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.01,0:30:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你送我這麼棒禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說…昨天在房間裡講的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.02,0:30:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.79,0:30:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.05,0:31:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…我今天可以早退嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.89,0:31:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得這麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.47,0:31:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.16,0:31:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.18,0:31:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.46,0:31:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼把那收拾乾淨你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.82,0:31:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.86,0:31:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.62,0:31:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嗎 你住在前男友那了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.61,0:31:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是了 提不上前男友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.42,0:31:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.28,0:31:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.41,0:31:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.85,0:31:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像有個女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.51,0:31:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不能很好表達自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.38,0:31:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法表達愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.97,0:31:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想我這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.17,0:31:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.24,0:31:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛美希哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.21,0:31:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你才會和千鶴…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.70,0:32:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.73,0:32:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了好過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.19,0:32:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.45,0:32:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.62,0:32:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.27,0:32:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回來 你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.40,0:32:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.02,0:32:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.57,0:33:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.97,0:33:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.86,0:33:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.67,0:33:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.69,0:33:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.11,0:33:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.09,0:33:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.54,0:33:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.23,0:33:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.47,0:33:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.61,0:33:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…昨天的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.70,0:33:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.57,0:33:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.93,0:34:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成悠大也…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.36,0:34:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有恐高症啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.09,0:34:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去東京塔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.06,0:34:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機師傅 請開快點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.37,0:34:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.97,0:34:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.05,0:34:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.46,0:34:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.78,0:34:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面 只看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.60,0:35:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.64,0:35:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叼著什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.33,0:35:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.06,0:35:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.51,0:35:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.70,0:35:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很危險 你小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.58,0:35:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話必須要傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.96,0:35:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 我做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.86,0:35:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.02,0:35:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.66,0:35:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.65,0:35:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.03,0:35:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.88,0:35:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我那麼任性
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.79,0:36:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.63,0:36:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.21,0:36:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.04,0:36:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠大…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.60,0:36:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.59,0:36:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.35,0:36:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型驢 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.11,0:36:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給悠大的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.76,0:36:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我找回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.69,0:36:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.79,0:36:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太危險 快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.13,0:37:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是 想著你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.43,0:37:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是在打工還是在家
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.54,0:37:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是不由自主地會想你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.22,0:37:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿不安
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.98,0:37:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.20,0:38:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.76,0:38:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你想像的那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.06,0:38:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.32,0:38:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.98,0:38:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安無事 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.38,0:38:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 要傳達給她 我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.19,0:38:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.04,0:38:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 剛剛下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.64,0:38:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.81,0:38:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.56,0:39:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是留言中心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.95,0:40:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.25,0:40:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…小型驢叼著的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.48,0:40:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給悠大
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.37,0:40:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.49,0:40:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.90,0:40:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.06,0:40:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.40,0:40:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是現在還是未來 今後永遠


